5/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>对明年<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>可能成为头条新闻的猜测做出了回应。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">英国流行乐队昨天（8 月 27 日）宣布将在英国和爱尔兰进行大型巡演</a>，名为“Oasis Live &#39;25”。这次徒步旅行定于 7 月和 8 月举行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔</a>将在 16 年来首次一起登台表演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-liam-noel-gallagher-3787549">你必须顺其自然：绿洲超音速回归的崎岖之路</a></strong></li></ul><p>这场备受期待的巡演目前在曼彻斯特希顿公园、伦敦温布利体育场、卡迪夫公国体育场、都柏林克罗克公园和爱丁堡默里菲尔德体育场进行多场演出。</p><p>由于需求巨大<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-reunion-tour-more-dates-rumoured-to-be-added-with-bonehead-reportedly-in-band-line-up-3788098">，预计很快就会增加即将举行的更多日期</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-plans-underway-for-2025-shows-outside-of-europe-3787647">在欧洲以外举办音乐会的计划目前也在进行中</a>。</p><p>目光敏锐的球迷很快注意到， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-oasis-be-headlining-glastonbury-2025-3787664">Oasis 的英国和爱尔兰站定于 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节结束后五天拉开帷幕</a>，这意味着加拉格尔乐队目前可以轻松登顶金字塔舞台。</p><p>然而，昨天的巡演公告称，确定的日期“将是乐队在欧洲的独家演出”。此外， <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/article/2024/aug/27/oasis-reunion-confirmed-for-uk-and-ireland-tour-in-2025-liam-noel-gallagher" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.somersetlive.co.uk/news/celebs-tv/oasis-not-headlining-20205-glastonbury-9511175" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《萨默塞特现场》</em></a>的报道也声称他们不会成为明年音乐节的头条新闻。</p><p>现在，Oasis 在社交媒体上发帖回应了有关 Glasto 的传闻。 “尽管有媒体猜测，Oasis 明年不会参加 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节或任何其他音乐节，”它开始说道。</p><p> “观看乐队表演的唯一方式是参加他们的 Oasis Live &#39;25 世界巡演。”请参阅下面的帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_NxyRPN1v_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551