ter-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里</a>（英国）和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.ie%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（爱尔兰）购买门票。粉丝们还可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-share-details-of-reunion-tour-pre-sale-ballot-sign-up-here-3787970">报名参加投票，以便在英国夏令时间今天 (28) 晚上 7 点之前周五 (30) 进行预售</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-2025-ticketmaster-share-strict-rules-for-buying-tickets-3787960">Ticketmaster 在销售前概述了购票的严格规定</a>，确认顾客每个家庭和卡只能订购四张门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3787542" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3787542" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3787542" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg" alt="Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 终于聚在一起，为 2025 年英国和爱尔兰体育场巡演的 Oasis 重聚。图片来源：Simon Emmett" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3787542" class="wp-caption-text"> Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 终于聚在一起，为 2025 年英国和爱尔兰体育场巡演的 Oasis 重聚。图片来源：Simon Emmett</figcaption></figure><h3> <strong>Oasis 2025 年英国和爱尔兰巡演日期为：</strong></h3><p><strong>七月</strong><br /><strong>04 – 卡迪夫，公国